{
  "texts": [
    "Syft decouples private data from model training using techniques such as FL, differential privacy, and encrypted computation.",
    "The OpenMined Syft community of frameworks is the most popular approach compared to the previous Tensor-Flow community frameworks.",
    "The Syft framework community represents a vision of an ecosystem for creating and developing private AI-powered solutions in a distributed and decentralized manner among data owners and data scientists (Sect. 2.2.4).",
    "1 3 PySyft PySyft (PySyft 2023) is the flagship of the OpenMined Syft community.",
    "PySyft augments DL frameworks for servers and IoT with privacy-preserving capabilities."
  ]
}